    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person\u2014it's in absolutely pristine condition and looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, keeping it garage-parked and spotless, so it still has that brand-new feel. It drives like a dream and is ready for a new home. I'm so excited for the next owner to enjoy it as much as I have! Drop me a message if you want to come by and take a look!",
